 "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么我们总怪父母没抓住房产和互联网红利，可轮到自己面对 AI 时代红利时，也没好好抓住？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在网上看到一句话，感叹万千：「这一刻突然懂了父亲当年的无奈，他站在改革开放的浪潮里，国家 GDP 翻了一百倍，可他为什么没赶上那班时代列车？如今我也站在 AI 浪潮下，大模型迭代不停，机会明明就在眼前，却抓不住风口。」 我们是不是错怪父母了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ea524a18068bbded86fd20e26e498eeb.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2035685308566610183"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExOTQxMzI0MSCOk/DPBjAAOJ8BQBByEzIwMzU2ODUzMDg1NjY2MTAxODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1778863899.782688", "card_id": "Q_1960414077269546321", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电纸书的唯一优点就是护眼了吧，其他感觉毫无优势，为什么卖这么贵？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近想入手电纸书，动辄几千，完全够买一个手机或者平板了，本来需求量就不大，为啥还要设这么贵？这不更没人买了吗？ 难道是因为技术要求高、制作困难？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-441716f6728f63ae6bde691da8eacbbf_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1960414077269546321"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExNjkxMjU5MCDC56jHBjAAOG5AEXITMTk2MDQxNDA3NzI2OTU0NjMyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778863899.783094", "card_id": "Q_8466955241", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 183}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何摆脱总是纠结「已经发生的事」的心态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有的时候总是纠结已经发生的事，觉得如果当时怎么怎么就好了。如何摆脱总是纠结已经发生的事的心态？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a934b14632d0042ca110c2af97d68a29_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8466955241"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExMjY2OTgxMSDH2dW7BjAAOJUCQBJyCjg0NjY5NTUyNDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778863899.783571", "card_id": "Q_2038577207740715513", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "外交部介绍美国总统特朗普访华情况，称「两国元首达成一系列新共识」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据外交部网站消息，外交部发言人就美国总统特朗普访华情况答记者问。 问：5 月 14 日，习近平主席为正在访华的美国总统特朗普举行系列国事活动，国内外高度关注。中方能否进一步介绍相关情况？ 答：应习近平主席邀请，美国总统特朗普正在对中国进行国事访问。这是中美两国元首继去年 10 月釜山之后再次面对面会晤，也是美国总统时隔 9 年再次访华。5 月 14 日，习近平主席为特朗普总统举行欢迎仪式和欢迎宴会，同特朗普总统举行会谈，并共同参观天坛。两国元首就事关两国和世界的重大问题深入交换意见，达成一系列新共识。 两国元首赞同将构建「中美建设性战略稳定关系」作为中美关系新定位，为未来 3 年乃至更长时间的中美关系提供战略指引，推动两国关系稳定、健康、可持续发展，为世界带来更多和平、繁荣、进步。 两国元首还就妥善处理彼此关切达成重要共识，同意就国际地区问题加强沟通和协调。 两国元首互动促进了相互理解，加深了彼此信任，推进了务实合作，增进了两国人民的福祉，为世界注入了亟需的稳定性和确定性。外交部发言人就美国总统特朗普访华情况答记者问 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4c318c2ae65c0c6e28ba8407dd9057ec.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038577207740715513"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExOTUxNDk2MSDZnZrQBjAAOF9AE3ITMjAzODU3NzIwNzc0MDcxNTUxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1778863899.784725", "card_id": "Q_2038548921241359825", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 108}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果深夜降价，17 Pro 系列首次进入 6000 元档位，17 到手 4499 元，怎样看待此次调价？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 15 日凌晨，苹果手机突然降价。京东 Apple 产品自营旗舰店显示，iPhone17 Pro 系列全线下调 1000 元，叠加以旧换新，双重补贴优惠 2000 元，到手价 6999 元，首次进入 6000 元档位。 iPhone17 更是迎来上市后首次降价，多重补贴以旧换新到手价只要 4499 元。 淘宝天猫 Apple Store 官方旗舰店同样调价，iPhone17 Pro 系列全线下调 1000 元，同样可叠加使用以旧换新优惠。 另据极目新闻，一苹果专卖店工作人员表示，授权店已收到通知。「每年 5 月份，很多果粉都在等这一波。本次会是全年优惠最大的一次活动。」他称，马上 618，这很可能是今年入手苹果手机的最佳时机。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-af8032dc68b75b30dd5e0e5db5d33be7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038548921241359825"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExOTUxMzEzMSCB6ZnQBjAAOKICQBRyEzIwMzg1NDg5MjEyNDEzNTk4MjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1778863899.785767", "card_id": "Q_2006125343182963479", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2026 年像 4B 、 7B 、 13B 这种大模型到底有什么使用场景？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ff455506bbceeabcd5a75cc8554814d1.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2006125343182963479"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIhemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCTExODQzNTA5NCCx/8HMBjAAOMIBQBVyEzIwMDYxMjUzNDMxODI5NjM0Nzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1778863899.786071", "card_id": "Q_272169012", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "法国人的性格是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "留学生一般跟法国人打交道的多吗？还是在中国人的圈子里面自己玩？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9277e48858f8d37674b625a91be3755_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/272169012"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ihemv9dm/5ZEFEAMaCDIyNzU2OTg1IMmVwdYFMAA4jwNAFnIJMjcyMTY5MDEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "s